description: Señor Blues is Las Vegas’ newest Food Truck to hit the streets, specializing in the ultimate Tex Mex! Senor Blues' motto is "Eat Organic…Eat Fresh, and Eat Homemade!"  This is not your typical fast food truck.  All of the cooking is done on site, and sauces are freshly prepared daily from scratch – making it truly gourmet mobile food. Try their Mucho Macho Nachos, the Blues Tacos, or one of their signature Burritos. Don't forget to "Make it Messy" with their homemade Enchilada sauce.
name: Senor Blues
